            2 años por escrito. Los precios son punto de partida — la cotización final es personalizada y gratuita.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          {s.paquetes.map((pkg) => {
            const isPopular = pkg.popular === true;
            const cardBg    = isPopular ? (isBrand ? 'bg-brand-500' : 'bg-accent-500') : 'bg-white';
            const nameCls   = isPopular ? 'text-white' : 'text-brand-500';
            const detailCls = isPopular ? 'text-white/75' : 'text-ink-500';
            const priceCls  = isPopular ? 'text-white' : 'text-brand-500';
            const borderCls = isPopular ? 'border-transparent shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(10,37,64,0.3)]' : 'border-cream-200';
            return (
              <article class={`card relative flex flex-col overflow-visible border ${borderCls} ${cardBg}`}>

                {/* Badge popular */}
                {isPopular && (
                  <div class="absolute -top-3.5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
                    <span class="rounded-full bg-accent-500 px-4 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white shadow-cta">
                      Más elegido
                    </span>
                  </div>
                )}

                <div class={`flex flex-1 flex-col p-6 ${isPopular ? 'pt-8' : ''}`}>

                  {/* Nombre paquete */}
                  <h3 class={`font-display text-[17px] font-black leading-snug ${nameCls}`}>
                    {pkg.name}
                  </h3>

                  {/* Precio */}
                  {pkg.precio ? (
                    <div class="mt-4">
                      <span class={`text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider ${isPopular ? 'text-white/60' : 'text-ink-400'}`}>desde</span>
                      <p class={`font-display text-3xl font-black leading-none ${priceCls}`}>
                        {formatPrice(pkg.precio)}
                      </p>
                      <span class={`text-[11px] ${isPopular ? 'text-white/50' : 'text-ink-400'}`}>MXN · todo incluido</span>
                    </div>
                  ) : (
                    <div class="mt-4">
                      <p class={`font-display text-xl font-black ${priceCls}`}>
                        Cotización personalizada
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  )}

                  {/* Separador */}
                  <div class={`my-5 h-px w-full ${isPopular ? 'bg-white/15' : 'bg-cream-200'}`}></div>

                  {/* Detalle */}
                  <p class={`flex-1 text-[13.5px] leading-relaxed ${detailCls}`}>
                    {pkg.detail}
                  </p>

                  {/* CTA */}
                  <a
                    href={`https://wa.me/${SITE.contact.whatsapp}?text=${encodeURIComponent(`Hola, me interesa el paquete "${pkg.name}" de ${s.title}.`)}`}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener"
                    class={`mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl py-3 text-[14px] font-bold transition-all ${
                      isPopular
                        ? 'bg-white text-brand-500 hover:bg-cream-50 hover:shadow-md'
                        : `border-2 ${isBrand ? 'border-brand-500 text-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-500 hover:text-white' : 'border-accent-500 text-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-500 hover:text-white'}`
                    }`}
                  >
                    Cotizar paquete
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </article>
            );
          })}
        </div>

        <!-- Nota inferior -->
        <p class="mt-6 text-center text-[13px] text-ink-400">
          ¿Necesitas algo diferente?
          <a href={`https://wa.me/${SITE.contact.whatsapp}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-semibold text-accent-500 hover:underline">Cuéntanos tu caso</a>
          y te damos una propuesta a la medida.
        </p>

      </div>
    </section>
  )}


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       6. FAQ + CONTACTO WHATSAPP — módulo unificado bicolumna
       ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  {s.faq.length > 0 && (
    <section class="section-cream" id="faq-contacto">
      <div class="container">

        <SectionHeader
          eyebrow="Preguntas + Contacto"
          title="Resuelve tu duda o cotiza al instante"
          highlight="cotiza al instante"
          level="lg"
          lead={[
            `Las <strong class="font-bold text-brand-500">preguntas frecuentes</strong> de la izquierda resuelven el 90% de las dudas que recibimos. Si la tuya no aparece, el formulario de la derecha abre WhatsApp directamente con un técnico CAMSEG certificado — sin formularios largos, sin call center, sin bots.`,
            `<strong class="font-semibold text-brand-500">Respuesta en menos de 15 minutos</strong> en horario hábil (Lun–Sáb 9:00–19:00). Para urgencias fuera de horario también respondemos, solo que el tiempo puede ser ligeramente mayor. Todas las consultas las atiende un técnico real, no un agente de ventas.`,
          ]}
        />

        <div class="mt-14 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-14 lg:items-start">

          <!-- ── COLUMNA IZQUIERDA — Acordeón FAQ ── -->
          <div class="space-y-3" id="faq-list">
            {s.faq.map((item, i) => (
              <details class="faq-item group rounded-2xl border border-cream-200 bg-white open:shadow-soft">
                <summary class="flex cursor-pointer select-none list-none items-start justify-between gap-4 p-5 text-[14.5px] font-bold text-ink-800 transition-colors hover:text-brand-500">
                  <span class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <span class={`mt-0.5 grid h-6 w-6 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full text-[11px] font-black text-white ${isBrand ? 'bg-brand-500' : 'bg-accent-500'}`}>
                      {i + 1}
                    </span>
                    {item.q}
                  </span>
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-ink-400 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/>
                  </svg>
                </summary>
                <div class="border-t border-cream-100 px-5 pb-5 pt-3">
                  <p class="pl-9 text-[14px] leading-[1.75] text-ink-600">{item.a}</p>
                </div>
              </details>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- ── COLUMNA DERECHA — Formulario WhatsApp + Datos directos ── -->
          <aside class="lg:sticky lg:top-32 lg:self-start">
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-brand-500 text-white shadow-[0_24px_60px_-20px_rgba(10,37,64,0.5)]">

              <!-- Header del módulo -->
              <div class={`border-b border-white/10 bg-brand-600 px-6 py-5`}>
                <p class="text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-accent-400">⚡ Cotización por WhatsApp</p>
                <h3 class="mt-1.5 font-display text-2xl font-black text-white">Cuéntanos tu caso</h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-cream-300">Abrimos WhatsApp con tu mensaje listo para enviar.</p>
              </div>

              <!-- Formulario compacto -->
              <form id={`waform-${slug}`} class="space-y-4 px-6 py-6" onsubmit="return false">
                <div>
                  <label for={`wa-nombre-${slug}`} class="mb-1.5 block text-[11.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white/70">Tu nombre</label>
                  <input type="text" id={`wa-nombre-${slug}`} placeholder="Ej. Carlos Ramírez" autocomplete="name"
                    class="w-full rounded-lg border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-[14px] text-white placeholder:text-white/35 transition focus:border-accent-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent-400" />
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                  <div>
                    <label for={`wa-zona-${slug}`} class="mb-1.5 block text-[11.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white/70">Zona / Ciudad</label>
                    <input type="text" id={`wa-zona-${slug}`} placeholder="Ej. CDMX"
                      class="w-full rounded-lg border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-[14px] text-white placeholder:text-white/35 transition focus:border-accent-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent-400" />
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label for={`wa-camaras-${slug}`} class="mb-1.5 block text-[11.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white/70">Cámaras aprox.</label>
                    <select id={`wa-camaras-${slug}`}
                      class="w-full rounded-lg border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-[14px] text-white transition focus:border-accent-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent-400">
                      <option class="bg-brand-700">No sé aún</option>
                      <option class="bg-brand-700">2 cámaras</option>
                      <option class="bg-brand-700">4 cámaras</option>
                      <option class="bg-brand-700">6-8 cámaras</option>
                      <option class="bg-brand-700">Más de 8</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <label for={`wa-msg-${slug}`} class="mb-1.5 block text-[11.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-white/70">
                    Cuéntanos más <span class="font-normal normal-case text-white/45">(opcional)</span>
                  </label>
                  <textarea id={`wa-msg-${slug}`} rows="3"
                    placeholder="Ej. Tengo una casa de 2 pisos con cochera..."
                    class="w-full resize-none rounded-lg border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-[14px] text-white placeholder:text-white/35 transition focus:border-accent-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent-400"></textarea>
                </div>

                <button type="button" data-waform-submit={slug} data-service-title={s.title} data-wa-phone={SITE.contact.whatsapp}
                  class="group flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-accent-500 px-6 py-4 font-display text-[15px] font-black text-white shadow-lg transition hover:bg-accent-600 hover:shadow-xl active:scale-[0.98]">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 0 1-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 0 1-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 0 1 2.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884"/>
                  </svg>
                  Enviar por WhatsApp
                </button>
                <p class="text-center text-[11.5px] text-cream-400">Respuesta en menos de 15 minutos · sin call center</p>
              </form>

              <!-- ── DATOS DIRECTOS ── -->
              <div class="border-t border-white/10 bg-brand-600 px-6 py-5">
                <p class="text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-accent-400 mb-4">Datos directos</p>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[13.5px]">
                    <span class="flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent-400" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 0 1-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 0 1-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 0 1 2.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                      <p class="text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-cream-400">WhatsApp</p>
                      <a href={`https://wa.me/${SITE.contact.whatsapp}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-white hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors">{SITE.contact.whatsappDisplay}</a>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[13.5px]">
                    <span class="flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent-400" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92Z"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                      <p class="text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-cream-400">Teléfono</p>
                      <a href={`tel:${SITE.contact.phone.replace(/\s/g, '')}`} class="text-white hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors">{SITE.contact.phone}</a>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[13.5px]">
                    <span class="flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent-400" aria-hidden="true">
                        <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-10 5L2 7"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                      <p class="text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-cream-400">Correo</p>
                      <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contact.email}`} class="text-white hover:text-accent-300 transition-colors break-all">{SITE.contact.email}</a>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[13.5px]">
                    <span class="flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent-400" aria-hidden="true">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
                      </svg>
                    </span>
                    <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                      <p class="text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-cream-400">Horario</p>
                      <p class="text-white">{SITE.contact.hours}</p>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </aside>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  )}

  <!-- WhatsApp form submit handler (shared para todos los slugs) -->
  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('[data-waform-submit]').forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const slug = btn.getAttribute('data-waform-submit');
        const serviceTitle = btn.getAttribute('data-service-title') || 'tu servicio';
        const nombre = (document.getElementById(`wa-nombre-${slug}`) as HTMLInputElement)?.value.trim() || 'un cliente';
        const zona = (document.getElementById(`wa-zona-${slug}`) as HTMLInputElement)?.value.trim();
        const camaras = (document.getElementById(`wa-camaras-${slug}`) as HTMLSelectElement)?.value;
        const msg = (document.getElementById(`wa-msg-${slug}`) as HTMLTextAreaElement)?.value.trim();

        let texto = `Hola, soy ${nombre}. Me interesa cotizar ${serviceTitle}`;
        if (camaras && camaras !== 'No sé aún') texto += `, aprox. ${camaras}`;
        if (zona) texto += `, en ${zona}`;
        texto += '.';
        if (msg) texto += ` ${msg}`;

        const phone = btn.getAttribute('data-wa-phone') || '525555555555';
        window.open(`https://wa.me/${phone}?text=${encodeURIComponent(texto)}`, '_blank');
      });
    });
  </script>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Quita el marcador nativo del summary */
  details summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  details summary::marker               { display: none; }

  /* Animación suave al abrir el details */
  details[open] .faq-body { animation: slide-down 0.2s ease; }
  @keyframes slide-down {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-6px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .faq-item[open] > summary {
    color: rgb(var(--color-brand));
  }
</style>
